<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="idc3165a83-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">1991—<ref href="/us/pl/102/83">Pub. L. 102–83</ref> renumbered <ref href="/us/usc/t38/s706">section 706 of this title</ref> as this section and substituted “Secretary” for “Administrator”.</p>
